Blockchain Braii and Chill is a relaxed, informal event series designed to bring together blockchain enthusiasts, developers, and innovators over a good braai (barbecue) to discuss all things blockchain and Web3. These gatherings provide a space to connect, learn, and share ideas about the latest trends, innovations, and challenges in the space—without the pressure of formal events. Whether you're new to blockchain or a seasoned pro, Blockchain Braii and Chill is all about fostering community, sparking conversations, and building relationships in a laid-back setting that encourages open dialogue and collaboration.
